Instructions for this assignment.

Installations:

crul:
sudo apt-get install curl

matplotlib:
python -mpip install -U pip
python -mpip install -U matplotlib

"sampel_topo.py" file should be under the folder "mininet" and you also need you execute the script "runTopology.sh" from this directory.

The files:
"OurLoadBalancer.py" should be under the folder "pox/ext" and you also need you execute the script "runPox.sh" from /pox directory.

In mininet terminal write:
xterm h5
xterm h6
xterm h7
xterm h8

in h5 terminal listen to port 80:
python3 -m http.server 80 &
xterm h6
in h6 terminal listen to port 80:
python3 -m http.server 80 &
xterm h7
in h7 terminal listen to port 80:
python3 -m http.server 80 &
xterm h8
in h8 terminal listen to port 80:
python3 -m http.server 80 &

h1 curl 10.1.2.3


Also: the clients can ping between themselves








